text:
Hello everyone I need some help with chat widget. I need to show/hide the chat widget on basis of loggedin user's role. I am calling
window.HubSpotConversations.widget.remove();
But what i need to call to show it again?

Like we do in intercom
```(window as any).Intercom("boot", {
  app_id: environment.Intercom.appId,
  name: UserModelUtil.getFullName(user),
  email: user.email,
});```
